---
---

<section class="py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-sand-100 to-sand-50" id="location">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-center text-lapis-900 mb-4">
      Nous Trouver
    </h2>
    <div class="w-24 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-saffron-500 to-transparent mx-auto mb-12"></div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-lapis-900 mb-4">Nayab Market Paris</h3>
        <p class="text-lapis-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Au cœur du 18ème arrondissement, à deux pas du métro La Chapelle et Marx Dormoy.
          Venez vivre l'expérience d'un véritable bazar afghan.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-white border-l-4 border-saffron-500 rounded-lg p-5 mb-4 shadow-md shadow-pomegranate-900/5">
          <strong class="block text-pomegranate-700 mb-1 font-semibold">📍 Adresse</strong>
          4 place de la Chapelle<br />75018 Paris, France
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-l-4 border-saffron-500 rounded-lg p-5 mb-4 shadow-md shadow-pomegranate-900/5">
          <strong class="block text-pomegranate-700 mb-1 font-semibold">🚇 Transports</strong>
          Métro <span class="font-semibold">La Chapelle</span> (ligne 2) · <span class="font-semibold">Marx Dormoy</span> (ligne 12)
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-l-4 border-saffron-500 rounded-lg p-5 mb-4 shadow-md shadow-pomegranate-900/5">
          <strong class="block text-pomegranate-700 mb-1 font-semibold">⏰ Horaires</strong>
          Lundi – Samedi : 9h00 – 21h00<br />Dimanche : 10h00 – 20h00
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-l-4 border-saffron-500 rounded-lg p-5 shadow-md shadow-pomegranate-900/5">
          <strong class="block text-pomegranate-700 mb-1 font-semibold">📦 Livraison</strong>
          Commandez en ligne, recevez chez vous partout en France.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <iframe
          src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=4+place+de+la+Chapelle+Paris&output=embed"
          width="100%"
          height="450"
          style="border:0; border-radius: 12px;"
          allowfullscreen
          loading="lazy"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
        ></iframe>
        <p class="mt-6 text-center">
          <a
            href="https://www.google.com/maps?q=4+place+de+la+Chapelle+Paris"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener"
            class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-br from-saffron-400 to-saffron-500 text-lapis-900 rounded-full font-semibold hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-saffron-500/40 transition"
          >
            Voir sur Google Maps →
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
